snippet.title: The Cave - Full Character Trailer
snippet.description:
The Cave will be available on January 22nd for the PlayStation Network, and the Nintendo eShop on Wii U for $14.99. On January 23rd, it will be available on Xbox LIVE Arcade for 1200 MSP, and Steam for $14.99. 

Meet all the characters in the upcoming Double Fine & Ron Gilbert adventure game!  

www.sega.com/thecave

ESRB Rating: Teen with Blood and Fantasy Violence.
